RecallPortalProductSummary is a SummaryForm
    title is "_"
    Layout
        header2 of "Product:_<ProductName>"
        single column
            ProductDescription
                use text area of 2 lines
        visible when (not RecallNotice.Equipment)
            three column
                ManufacturerInformation.ManufacturerNumber
                VendorItem
                GlobalTradeItemNumber
                UPC
                UPN1
                UPN2
                SKU
                NDC
        visible when (RecallNotice.Equipment)
            single column
                ModelNumber
